American Cyanamid Co said it boughtthe 50 pct interest of Cyanamid Fothergill Ltd held by&lt;Fothergill and Harvey PLC>, making the unit a wholly ownedsubsidiary.    The unit manufactures structural materials, includingadvanced composites, adhesives, and aluminum honeycomb for theEuropean space industry.    The current management will remain in place and the unitwill continue at its locations in Wrexham, U.K., the companysaid. Reuter&#3;